<tr>
  <td style="padding-bottom: 10px">Dear <%= name %>,</td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td style="padding-bottom: 10px">
    We received a request to reset the password associated with your account on
    NOVASPHERE. If you did not request a password reset, please disregard this
    email. Otherwise, follow the instructions below to reset your password.
  </td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td style="padding-bottom: 10px"><strong>Reset Your Password</strong></td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td style="padding-bottom: 10px">
    Click the link below to reset your password:
  </td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td style="padding-bottom: 10px">
    <a href="<%= resetLink %>"><%= resetLink %></a>
  </td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td style="padding-bottom: 10px">
    If the above link doesn't work, please copy and paste the following URL into
    your web browser:
  </td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td style="padding-bottom: 10px"><%= resetLink %></td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td style="padding-bottom: 10px">
    <strong>Important Security Information</strong>
  </td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td style="padding-bottom: 10px">
    For your security, this link will expire in 24 hours. If you do not reset
    your password within this timeframe, you will need to submit a new password
    reset request.
  </td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td style="padding-bottom: 10px">
    If you have any questions or need further assistance, please contact our
    support team at
    <a href="mailto:support@novasphere.com">support@novasphere.com</a> or call
    01-6310962.
  </td>
</tr>
